{"tid":1278320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣香港網絡民主連線","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T03:33:19.000Z","uid":59818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf8366dd7b27734b07ee3cad1bd60c0643b142d","tid":1278320,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:03:17.000Z","msg":"啱啱係連登見個有個台灣巴打開post<br />\n<br />\n「港台連線」我是台灣人，對不起我昨天沒膽進香港立法院<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277599</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好感激佢 覺得佢可以再搞大啲 例如開個Facebook Instagram page, 去返台灣論壇開post <br />\n<br />\n另外我地都可以上返台灣嘅論壇開啲你問我答post<br />\n或者share 下連登同埋其他香港人嘅諗法 例如琴日衝嘅時侯 唔同人有咩意見<br />\n<br />\n有啲野台媒未必會報咁仔細 例如義士琴日同毛ee嘅對話/立場姐姐同妹妹同對話等<br />\n<br />\n如果有個香港人親自同台灣嘅人講野 相信會提升台灣對香港嘅關注"},{"pid":"fc82c1aaae157fc9d84e4bffa789a5e2b17d2c8a","tid":1278320,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcaf65a7bd358dbd74e7b97c8f5d8fa68d4ff16","tid":1278320,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61adc0e2efd1db6c89aa3d2df50701434dd41303","tid":1278320,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3cb52f86e347426ba3f2bffec6f211749be187","tid":1278320,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:29:10.000Z","msg":"［文宣戰對準台灣］蔡英文要做多d助攻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282101</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8a1482c2848d64da77afb39277c8cf2da8b5894","tid":1278320,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:30:05.000Z","msg":"巴打好好呀呢個建議<br />\n立場